{"tid":1727823,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"唔知點答點解塞路？入嚟俾個簡單答案你","createTime":"2019-11-16T14:50:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T17:39:51.000Z","uid":53610,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a2a1471492411b749f6f052e5b2ea8e022fc7c82","tid":1727823,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:50:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">因為毒氣彌漫囉</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6x53mif.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6x53mif.jpg&h=19026939&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lvm91if.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLvm91if.png&h=ddd116f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s9RBGig.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs9RBGig.png&h=362d2ba6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港依家周圍都係毒氣，四處都係二噁英<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點解政府仲要人返工</span></span><br />\n係咪唔當市民條命係命？<br />\n出面槍林彈雨，空氣又有毒，根本唔適宜出街，亦唔應該返工<br />\n<br />\n手足塞得嗰啲路都係毒氣重災區，啲人經過吸一啖都唔知要幾多年先分解到<br />\n<br />\n家陣手足們冒著生命危險阻止一般市民吸入毒氣，何罪之有？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一日最衰都係政府，全港飄住毒氣都唔停工停市</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋應該將毒氣警告文宣貼滿全香港，所有燈柱、欄杆、牆壁甚至地板都要遍佈溫馨提示<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">提醒市民小心毒氣，儘量留喺屋企</span></span>"},{"pid":"8fc5933c14b7e971735a3c3e50976aaa49d382d7","tid":1727823,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:57:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">示威者提醒清除路障市民<br />\n現場毒氣彌漫<br />\n吸入會損害身體健康<br />\n建議戴上口罩</span>"},{"pid":"3ef71495a27c3bcf9cfa018a963f235579d2aa30","tid":1727823,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:58:05.000Z","msg":"因間推"},{"pid":"44659aea405f41c0483a3b7a4805744d8e17ca17","tid":1727823,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T17:04:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab9d97870c524594d8370996f7565b5d8a066410","tid":1727823,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T17:05:22.000Z","msg":"塞路係手段唔係目的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5eeb5afcf239d7bff5a6052366469e006a4721","tid":1727823,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:39:51.000Z","msg":"推"}]}